---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import GeneralHero from "@/components/HeroSections/GeneralHero.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <GeneralHero title="Terms of Service" />
  <!-- Start of Team Details  section
	============================================= -->
    <section
    id="ori-team-details"
    class="ori-team-details-section position-relative"
>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="ori-team-details-content">
            <div class="ori-team-personal-info-wrapper">
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>Terms and Conditions</h3>
                    <h2 class="date">Last Updated: 17 JAN, 2025</h2>
                    <p>
                        Welcome to Devliqly! These Terms and Conditions govern your use of
                        our services. By engaging with Devliqly, you agree to comply with
                        these terms. If you do not agree, please refrain from using our
                        services.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>1. Introduction</h3>
                    <p>
                        Devliqly provides professional technical services, including Web
                        Development, AI Development, Game Development, SEO, and Graphic
                        Design. These Terms outline the rights and responsibilities of
                        both Devliqly and the client.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>2. Scope of Services</h3>
                    <p>
                        We offer a range of services, including but not limited to:
                        <p class="list">
                            &bull; Custom Website and Web Application Development (Frontend & Backend)
                            <br />
                            &bull; AI Development and Automation Solutions
                            <br />
                            &bull; Game Development (2D, 3D, and Web-based games)
                            <br />
                            &bull; UI/UX and Graphic Design
                            <br />
                            &bull; SEO Optimization & Digital Marketing
                            <br />
                            &bull; Google Business Profile Optimization
                            <br />
                            &bull; Ad Campaign Management
                            <br />
                        </p>
                        <p class="bottom-text">Our services are tailored to the specific requirements of each client.</p>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>3. Project Engagement Process</h3>
                    <h2 class="date">3.1 Consultation and Agreement</h2>
                    <p>
                        Devliqly provides professional technical services, including Web
                        Development, AI Development, Game Development, SEO, and Graphic
                        Design. These Terms outline the rights and responsibilities of
                        both Devliqly and the client.
                    </p>
                    <h2 class="date">3.2 Development and Feedback</h2>
                    <p>
                        Regular updates and prototypes are shared for feedback. Clients are
                        expected to provide timely feedback to avoid project delays.
                    </p>
                    <h2 class="date">3.3 Completion and Handover</h2>
                    <p>
                        Final project delivery is done upon successful testing and client
                        approval. Any post-delivery modifications are subject to additional
                        costs unless otherwise agreed.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>4. Payment Terms</h3>
                    <h2 class="date">4.1 Payment Structure</h2>
                    <p>
                        25% of the total project cost is due upon presentation of the first
                        working prototype. The remaining balance will be paid in agreed-upon
                        milestones or upon final project completion.
                    </p>
                    <h2 class="date">4.2 Payment Methods</h2>
                    <p>
                        Payments can be made via bank transfer, UPI, or other agreed-upon
                        methods. All invoices must be cleared within the stipulated due date
                        to avoid delays.
                    </p>
                    <h2 class="date">4.3 Refund Policy</h2>
                    <p>
                        Payments made are non-refundable unless Devliqly fails to deliver
                        the agreed-upon scope. If the client decides to terminate the project,
                        payments already made will not be refunded.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>5. Client Responsibilities</h3>
                    <p class="list">
                        &bull; Provide clear and complete project requirements before commencement.
                        <br />
                        &bull; Ensure timely feedback and approval of deliverables.
                        <br />
                        &bull; Make payments as per the agreed schedule to avoid project halts.
                        <br />
                        &bull; Obtain necessary permissions/licenses for content, third-party
                        assets, or APIs used in the project.
                        <br />
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>6. Intellectual Property & Ownership</h3>
                    <p>
                        Devliqly retains ownership of all work-in-progress until full payment
                        is received. Upon final payment, the client gains full rights to the
                        delivered project, excluding third-party tools or licensed assets.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We reserve the right to showcase completed projects in our portfolio
                        unless explicitly stated otherwise by the client.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>7. Confidentiality</h3>
                    <p>
                        Both parties agree to keep confidential information private and not
                        disclose it to third parties. Sensitive business information shared by
                        the client will be protected under strict confidentiality policies.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>8. Revisions and Support</h3>
                    <p>
                        A fixed number of revisions will be included based on the project
                        agreement. Post-delivery support is available for a limited time,
                        after which additional support will be chargeable. Any feature
                        enhancements beyond the agreed scope will be treated as a new project
                        or an additional cost.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>9. Liability & Disclaimers</h3>
                    <p>
                        Devliqly is not responsible for third-party service failures, hosting
                        issues, or software bugs beyond our control. We do not guarantee search
                        engine rankings or ad campaign results. Any damages resulting from misuse
                        or unauthorized modifications of the project are not our liability.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>10. Termination Policy</h3>
                    <p>
                        Either party may terminate the project if the other party fails to meet
                        obligations. Devliqly reserves the right to terminate a project if the
                        client breaches these Terms. Any outstanding payments must be settled
                        before termination.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>11. Governing Law & Dispute Resolution</h3>
                    <p>
                        These Terms shall be governed by the laws of India. Any disputes arising
                        will first be resolved through mutual discussion. If unresolved, disputes
                        will be handled through arbitration in New Delhi.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>12. Amendments to Terms</h3>
                    <p>
                        Devliqly reserves the right to update these Terms at any time. Clients
                        will be notified of significant changes.
                    </p>
                    <p>By using our services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to these Terms and Conditions. For any queries, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact.devliqly@gmail.com"><b>contact.devliqly@gmail.com</b></a>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="line_animation">
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
    </div>
</section>

  <!-- End of Team Details  section
	============================================= -->
</Layout>
<style>
  .date {
    font-size: 20px;
    padding-top: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .list{
    padding-top: 10px;
    margin-left: 18px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    /* margin-bottom: 0; */
  }
 
</style>
